# User Messages
msgid "Welcome, {username}! Your account has been created successfully."
msgstr "Xush kelibsiz, {username}! Hisobingiz muvaffaqiyatli yaratildi."

msgid ""
"As an author, you must read and accept our article writing rules before "
"publishing."
msgstr ""
"Muallif sifatida siz nashr etishdan oldin maqola yozish qoidalarimizni "
"o'qib, qabul qilishingiz kerak."

msgid "Registration failed. Please correct the errors below."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxatdan o'tish muvaffaqiyatsiz tugadi. Quyidagi xatolarni tuzating."

msgid "Invalid username or password. Please try again."
msgstr "Noto'g'ri foydalanuvchi nomi yoki parol. Qayta urinib ko'ring."

msgid "You have been logged out successfully."
msgstr "Tizimdan muvaffaqiyatli chiqdingiz."

msgid "Access denied. This page is only for authors."
msgstr "Kirish rad etildi. Bu sahifa faqat mualliflar uchun."

msgid ""
"Article rules have not been configured yet. Please contact the "
"administrator."
msgstr ""
"Maqola qoidalari hali sozlanmagan. Iltimos, administrator bilan bog'laning."

msgid "Thank you for accepting the rules! You can now create articles."
msgstr ""
"Qoidalarni qabul qilganingiz uchun rahmat! Endi maqolalar yaratishingiz "
"mumkin."

msgid "You must accept the rules to proceed."
msgstr "Davom etish uchun qoidalarni qabul qilishingiz kerak."

msgid "Please accept the article writing rules to start publishing."
msgstr "Nashr etishni boshlash uchun maqola yozish qoidalarini qabul qiling."

msgid "Please log in to access this page."
msgstr "Ushbu sahifaga kirish uchun tizimga kiring."

msgid "Access denied. Only authors can create articles."
msgstr "Kirish rad etildi. Faqat mualliflar maqola yaratishi mumkin."

msgid "You must accept the article writing rules before creating articles."
msgstr ""
"Maqola yaratishdan oldin maqola yozish qoidalarini qabul qilishingiz kerak."

msgid "Access denied. You can only edit your own articles."
msgstr "Kirish rad etildi. Faqat o'z maqolalaringizni tahrirlashingiz mumkin."

msgid "Access denied. You can only delete your own articles."
msgstr "Kirish rad etildi. Faqat o'z maqolalaringizni o'chirishingiz mumkin."

